Author: TheShortGerman
Text: No kidding, I feel like fucking death. I’m really new to purging, I was restrictive only in the past but have B/P tendencies with this relapse. I just purged for an hour and a half straight and still didn’t get it all out, I don’t know how people do this all the time. I purged out over 6 lbs worth of food and fluids.

Author: iamghostgal
Text: maybe your body isn't used to it. its okay. you can try again another time.   i hope you feel ok, purging that much takes a lot out of you.
